This paper deals with deep neural networks and their performance in image classification, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also addresses the issue of noisy labels, which is a common problem in natural language processing (cs.CL) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Therefore, these five categories are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
